---
// src/pages/providers/index.astro
// B2B page — for signing up removal companies
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Cane Toad Removal Leads for Florida Providers | CaneToadFL Partner Program"
  description="Are you a licensed cane toad or bufo toad removal provider in South Florida? Join our network and receive qualified leads from homeowners actively searching for removal service."
>

  <div class="hero">
    <h1>Get Qualified Cane Toad Removal Leads in Your Service Area</h1>
    <p>We generate leads from South Florida homeowners actively searching for cane toad removal. You pay only when you receive a qualified lead — name, phone, and address of someone ready to book service.</p>
    <a href="#provider-form" class="btn btn-lg">Apply to Join Our Network →</a>
  </div>

  <div class="content">

    <h2>How It Works</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>We capture the lead</strong> — homeowners find us via Google and submit their contact info and address</li>
      <li><strong>We route by zip code</strong> — leads are sent to matched providers in that area within minutes</li>
      <li><strong>You close the job</strong> — you receive an email and SMS with the lead details and follow up directly</li>
      <li><strong>We bill weekly</strong> — transparent reporting, call recordings as proof of delivery</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Why Partner With Us</h2>
    <p>At $190 for an initial visit and $170/month for recurring service, a single customer is worth $1,200–$2,000+ over their first year. Our leads are high-intent — these are homeowners actively searching for removal, not cold outreach. The economics work.</p>

    <h2>Lead Pricing</h2>
    <p>Shared leads (sent to up to 2 providers): <strong>$40–$50/lead</strong><br/>
    Exclusive leads (sent to you only): <strong>$60–$75/lead</strong></p>
    <p>Minimum commitment: 10 leads/month. Cancel with 30 days notice.</p>

    <h2>Who We Work With</h2>
    <p>We work with FWC-registered nuisance wildlife trappers who specialize in or regularly perform cane toad removal. We do not work with general pest control companies who list toad removal as an afterthought.</p>

    <h2>Apply to Join</h2>

  </div>

  <div class="lead-form-wrap" id="provider-form">
    <h2>Provider Application</h2>
    <p>Tell us about your business and service area. We'll follow up within 24 hours.</p>
    <iframe data-tally-src="https://tally.so/embed/q4OA65?alignLeft=1&hideTitle=1&transparentBackground=1&dynamicHeight=1" width="100%" height="320" frameborder="0" marginheight="0" marginwidth="0" title="Provider Application Form"></iframe>
  </div>

</BaseLayout>
